{"tid":2456584,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有啲差佬心理真係扭曲","createTime":"2021-03-22T05:05:45.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-22T05:40:03.000Z","uid":363330,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"701293ad7b5a719aafa56ab888812a1f3e70ea57","tid":2456584,"uid":363330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T05:05:45.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n<br />\n喺街行緊 一路睇緊Google Maps<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n迎面有兩件喺度行緊咇 當然佢哋係拍埋一齊行<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我咩點理佢哋 反正我靠右佢靠左 條路又闊<br />\n咁我就繼續睇地圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/read.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n行多兩行我再抬頭望<br />\n其中一個企開咗 喺我正面約三步左右<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n即係我遲抬頭多一秒就會相撞<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我心諗係咪真係咁無聊呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n條路夠4個人一字排開<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你想企鬆啲都冇話走到去對頭車嘅路線度呱<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/nope.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁係咪想引我撞你然後畀你撒賴先<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2c521fd99ffe16c3fbff315040a8d014af0d541","tid":2456584,"uid":71657,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T05:08:09.000Z","msg":"有啲？<br />\n樓豬瞓撚咗幾耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd8e3efc637f2e9a2740fc12ed15f1df0251198a","tid":2456584,"uid":359598,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T05:10:40.000Z","msg":"可以同你講佢哋真係咁無聊 你諗返佢哋學歷去到邊"},{"pid":"be274a07a68a67c2e8ce9cff3a01f281e5b8f9e2","tid":2456584,"uid":54579,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T05:13:41.000Z","msg":"你諗下佢地咁得鳩閒，唔搵呢d野玩點過日神"},{"pid":"d910763b7575b27afa841ca027bd8596deb976ef","tid":2456584,"uid":393145,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T05:17:31.000Z","msg":"兩件行咇算好<br />\n依家成日5 6隻一定行咇<br />\n屌一排橫行霸撚晒成條行人路<br />\n啲人行唔到<br />\n出馬路又俾佢屌賞花杏仁露<br />\non撚99"},{"pid":"6fdd2ec82eb65bc1d9d40ee307815a89eb972f69","tid":2456584,"uid":363330,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"f2c521fd99ffe16c3fbff315040a8d014af0d541","tid":2456584,"uid":71657,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T05:08:09.000Z","msg":"有啲？<br />\n樓豬瞓撚咗幾耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T05:17:50.000Z","msg":"標題改過嚟刪漏咗個有字啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23df2eb459ce172823cf3c3c1c11f9fec3201505","tid":2456584,"uid":165136,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T05:18:12.000Z","msg":"低級警員就係咁幼稚<br />\n到退休嗰d 平日生活對親戚都係志在玩人, 顯示自己權力<br />\n屌返佢一係就話你唔玩得<br />\n一係當自己無講過大大聲屌返你無證據屈佢<br />\n再唔係就話本身好少事當解決咗唔好提, 但你態度唔好屌返你"},{"pid":"716511afae05545afa23b488eae1ec3b04471c64","tid":2456584,"uid":50521,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T05:22:46.000Z","msg":"點解而家ｄ黑警禁撚討厭，真係有原因。"},{"pid":"8a5a2b1616f1bf39eff632d7201675fd3e1ecf13","tid":2456584,"uid":363330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"23df2eb459ce172823cf3c3c1c11f9fec3201505","tid":2456584,"uid":165136,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T05:18:12.000Z","msg":"低級警員就係咁幼稚<br />\n到退休嗰d 平日生活對親戚都係志在玩人, 顯示自己權力<br />\n屌返佢一係就話你唔玩得<br />\n一係當自己無講過大大聲屌返你無證據屈佢<br />\n再唔係就話本身好少事當解決咗唔好提, 但你態度唔好屌返你"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-2